A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Article 1 of Chapter 2 of Title 20 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
2 relating to the State Board of Education, so as to require the Georgia Department of
3 Education to complete a study within 90 days of any action by any branch of the federal
4 government that results in certain reductions of the scope, workforce, or budget of the United
5 States Department of Education to determine the impact on public schools in this state; to
6 provide for reporting; to authorize the department to contract with a nonpartisan independent
7 entity to conduct such study; to provide definitions; to provide for a short title; to provide for
8 related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
9 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
10 SECTION 1.
11 This Act shall be known and may be cited as the "Education Impact Transparency Act."
12 SECTION 2.
13 Article 1 of Chapter 2 of Title 20 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to the
14 State Board of Education, is amended by adding a new Code section to read as follows:
